'''ADI 4277 and ADPF 132''' (May 5, 2011), are landmark [[Supreme Court of Brazil|Brazil Supreme Court]] cases.
==Rights== After of the decision of the Supreme Court, the same 112 rights of different-sex marriages were given to same-sex stable relationships too, creating a [[de facto]] [[civil union]] system, including the most important:<ref>[http://noticias.r7.com/brasil/noticias/supremo-tribunal-federal-reconhece-uniao-estavel-gay-20110506.html 112 rights to Brazilian same-sex couples {{pt icon}}]</ref> *[[LGBT adoption|Adoption]] *[[Inheritance]] *[[Pension]] *[[Health plan]]
